Sentencas: The structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 (LSMO) films for electrode applications were investigated as a function of annealing temperature.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3

Sentencas: Mesoporous LSMO films were successfully synthesized by using sol-gel and evaporation-induced self-assembly processes.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3

Sentencas: Metal acetates and Brij-S10 were used as the starting material and pore structure-forming template, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3

Sentencas: With the adoption of mesoporous structure in the LSMO film, the surface area of mesoporous LSMO films was increased up to 165% with an annealing temperature increase from 350 to 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity value of mesoporous LSMO was determined to be 46 S/cm at a measurement temperature of 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3

Sentencas: This greatly increased the surface area and provided reasonable electrical conductivity, which makes mesoporous LSMO films suitable as electrode materials of micro-solid oxide fuel cell devices.
Titulo: Effect of annealing temperature on the structural and electrical properties of mesoporous La0.7Sr0.3MnO3
